org.dcm4che3.sample.osgi.device.impl

Class EchoDeviceServiceImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dcm4che3.net.DeviceService
      • org.dcm4che3.sample.osgi.device.impl.EchoDeviceServiceImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DeviceServiceInterface, EchoDeviceService

    public class EchoDeviceServiceImpl
extends DeviceService
implements EchoDeviceService
    Bundle implementing and starting a generic Dicom Device. Start method is defined in blueprint.xml, and invoked by the Blueprint Container. This bundle will be injected in every Dicom Service bundles, which will use it to register themselves in the device.
    Author:
    Umberto Cappellini
